	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=43455><span id= >Kameni</span></a><br><span id=notbold>8 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>At your level, you probably don't need to stress out too much about your wt restriction.&nbsp;&nbsp;Its a good habit to get into to be checking your weight, but if you happen to get your hands on a piece or two of leather easily, you could certainly wear it for the time being.  As mentioned previously, make sure to get cured/raw silk as soon as you can, or netted from the froglocks in Qey sewers.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
