	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=43455><span id= >Kameni</span></a><br><span id=notbold>8 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>You can only use one special attack per round, regardless whether it is a hand attack or a kick attack.<br><br>I'm not absolutely sure, but I believe the same goes for disciplines, you can only use 1 at a time, and (check me on this one) you cannot use another until your reuse time is up.&nbsp;&nbsp;For most disciplines, this is approximately an hour until level 60, so basically you get 10 seconds of any discipline once per hour.  The first discipline a monk gets is the resist discipline at level 30, then I believe the next disciplines are at 40, 50, 51... and so on.  Check some links, there is some very good information regarding disciplines out there.  <br><br>As far as your expansion goes, you will need to get Velious before you can activate any of these disciplines.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
