	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=36958><span id=Scholar>Beemo</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>171 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Remember to always turn off your attack before you feign.&nbsp;&nbsp;It will not work unless you do this.<br><br>A good starting monk item is Essence of Dol.  Its 10/28 5dex and 0.1 wt.  I bought mine off someone for 73pp and used it until I was duel wielding Fighting Batons.  Its an off hand weapon only wich is actually a good thing because it lets you work your hth and the added dex increases the rate your attack skills increase.<br><br>Don't ignore 2HB!!!! Have a shaman or Mage summon you a dimensional hole and keep a worn great staff in it.  A good strategy I use is to wait till a mob starts to run away and switch to my 2HB and get a couple whacks in.  DON'T keep anything of value in the dimensional hole or it poofs!</p>&nbsp;<br>Quanko Crakkers<br>63 Grandmaster<br>(Elan Vitale)<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87045" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87045</a><br>Xegony</td></td></tr>
